    "description": "<strong>《Cozy Dungeons》</strong>是一款冒险/室内设计游戏，你需要探索地牢、清除敌人并翻新地牢以获取利润！成为怪物灭绝公会的领导者，为自己的主业增添一点装修内容。毕竟，既可以征服地牢，又可以把它变成民宿，何乐而不为呢？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索危险的地牢</h2>在充满刁钻谜题、险恶敌人和致命陷阱的地牢中寻找出路。使用各种工具来帮助你探索和战斗，但记得保持警觉——因为工具的作用只是让你更有可能活下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/df1bf2d2d6cd8af4c97e939bade55fd7.poster.avif?t=1757096974\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/df1bf2d2d6cd8af4c97e939bade55fd7.webm?t=1757096974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >释放你内心的革新精神</h2>你到访的每一个地牢都属于一位客户，他们希望地牢看起来焕然一新！打造新家具，清除垃圾，更换墙壁和地板，出售破损的家具等等！等一切就绪，金币就会滚滚而来！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/965184e5e6e3e5abc8095391abdaac3a.poster.avif?t=1757096974\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/965184e5e6e3e5abc8095391abdaac3a.webm?t=1757096974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义你的公会</h2>你可以按自己的方式，用辛苦赚来的金币来装饰和扩张公会，升级角色，购买新图纸，结识新朋友等等——一切皆有可能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/1b02dd524c59bc01a8aacde3e9d09e62.poster.avif?t=1757096974\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377600/extras/1b02dd524c59bc01a8aacde3e9d09e62.webm?t=1757096974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
